datasaurus_dozen %>%
  group_by(dataset) %>%
  summarize(
    mean_x = mean(x),
    sd_x = sd(x),
    mean_y = mean(y),
    sd_y = sd(y),
    cor = cor(x,y)
  )

  ggplot(aes(x = x, y = y)) +
  geom_point(aes(colour=dataset)) +
  geom_smooth(method = "lm", se = FALSE) +
  facet_wrap(~dataset, ncol = 3, scales = "free")+
  guides(colour=FALSE)+
  theme_minimal()
